    <title>MaximumAirflowDeltaVsTPS_07A59E</title>
    <description>Purpose: Table of delta MAF values as a function of desired throttle position. The output of this table provides a delta MAF that if the measured minus the estimated MAP exceeds, is considered a fail. It is intended to be calibrated with smaller deltas at lower throttle position. Axes: X - Table of breakpoints for KtTPSD_dm_MAF_DesThrDelt and KtTPSD_p_MAP_DesThrDelt tables. Format: 1x9; 16-bit big-endian unsigned integer; Y = X * 0.0078125; units g/s. Source: KtTPSD_dm_MAF_DesThrDelt at 0x078AEE in winols_astra.csv. Astra mapping/local notes: Confirmed HP Tuners Airflow Correlation P0068 Airflow Delta / [ECM] 14044 Maximum Airflow Delta vs. TPS equivalent. WinOLS/Damos symbol KtTPSD_dm_MAF_DesThrDelt. Source Corsa/HP Tuners fingerprint at 0x07BFEE maps by table-to-table offset -0x1A50 to this Astra table at 0x07A59E; Damos source 0x078AEE maps by local TPSD shift +0x1AB0. 1x9 unsigned 16-bit big-endian, scaled X / 128.</description>
