    <title>TCS_PresenceConfig_079BB8</title>
    <description>Exact TCSI configuration pair: KeTCSI_b_TCS_Present followed by KeTCSI_b_UseSerialData. Stock values are 0 and 1, so the ECM uses serial data from the EBCM and ignores the false fallback. Changing Use Serial Data to 0 while leaving TCS Present Fallback at 0 forces the ECM-side TCS-present result false. This may affect network diagnostics and still does not disable brake intervention inside the EBCM.</description>
